Python Project: Text-based Adventure game

Requirements for this Udacity project: 
- The game gives players a description of what's happening, and then asks them for input
- Something different happens based on the choice the player made
- The game includes some random factors
- The game has conditions for winning and losing
- When the game is over, it asks if the player wants to play again
- The game validates input of the user
- the code is refactored
- the code complies with pycodestyle

Instructions: 
please open the python file, for example using git Bash and enter your input according to the 
text appearing. Enjoy :) 